<div><head>籟紀．敘</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_001-1a.2">夫一元上始，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_001-1a.3">無聲臭也；<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_001-1a.4">二氣方析，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_001-1a.5">斯喘動哉。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_001-1a.6">是以乾坤畫而風雷至，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_001-1a.7">往復定而律呂存。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_001-1a.8">人肖玄樞，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_001-1a.9">耳為感際，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_001-1a.10">故聆虛器則潮震，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_001-1a.11">語空山則谷應。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_001-1a.12">蓋有形斯氣，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_001-1a.13">有氣斯響，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_001-1a.14">靡往弗充接之在有也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_001-1a.15">予遭變故以來，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_001-1a.16">骨肉奄已漂淪，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_001-1a.17">氣焰頓乎消歇。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_001-1a.18">裸將京邑，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_001-1a.19">夢寐丘陵，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_001-1a.20">既慚瓜美青門，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_001-1a.21">秪哭黍離白下，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_001-1a.22">故雖強對妻孥，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_001-1a.23">都非舊態。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_001-1a.24">行坐臥起，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_001-1a.25">觸耳成悲，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_001-1a.26">古人云樂一也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_001-1a.27">喜者聽之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_001-1a.28">喜悲者聽之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_001-1a.29">悲豈靈造之變更，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_001-1a.30">亦人心之遷適也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_001-1a.31">爰取莊子三籟之義，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_001-1a.32">嗣采史傳八風之言，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_001-1a.33">附諸有聲，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_001-1a.34">彙為一筴，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_001-1a.35">將以上胤麥秀之音，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_001-1a.36">下攄離騷之感，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_001-1a.37">冀同遇者之覽觀，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_001-1a.38">非敢語于中和之君子矣。<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
<div><head>籟紀．天籟卷之上</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-1a" ed="CHANT" n="002-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-1a.2">條風</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-1a.3">一曰炎風。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-1a.4">起自變天方土之蒼門。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-1a.5">從東北來。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-1a.6">陳子聞而賦之曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-1a.7">「噫條風之沕穆兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-1a.8">出萬物而條治。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-1a.9">釋寒冰而方堅兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-1a.10">吁陳荄於既死。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-1a.11">睹澌流之汛汛兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-1a.12">羨方舟之南逝感群類之有復兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-1a.13">哀吾生之終否。」<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-2a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-2a" ed="CHANT" n="002-2a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-2a.2">明庶風</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-2a.3">一曰谷風。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-2a.4">起自界天開明之門。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-2a.5">從東方來。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-2a.6">陳子聞而賦之曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-2a.7">「噫谷風之習習兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-2a.8">明眾物而殫出。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-2a.9">粲芳春之韶豔兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-2a.10">疇𦾶𦾶其秀麥。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-2a.11">審雨露之有期兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-2a.12">懼芬華之頓息。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-2a.13">時冉冉其告嘗兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-2a.14">痛皇考之不食。」<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-3a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-3a" ed="CHANT" n="002-3a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-3a.2">清明風</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-3a.3">起自陽天波毋之門。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-3a.4">從東南來。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-3a.5">陳子聞而賦之曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-3a.6">「噫清明之振振兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-3a.7">吹萬物而西適。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-3a.8">覽動植之向榮兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-3a.9">念予降於五日。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-3a.10">緊始&amp;CH-0F0227;而邦之蔡兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-3a.11">壯齊戶而帝陟曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-3a.12">予受命于天兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-3a.13">豈公子之我失。」<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-4a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-4a" ed="CHANT" n="002-4a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-4a.2">景風</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-4a.3">一曰凱風，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-4a.4">又曰薰風，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-4a.5">亦曰巨風。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-4a.6">起自赤天之暑門。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-4a.7">從南方來。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-4a.8">陳子聞而賦之曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-4a.9">「噫飄颻之景風兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-4a.10">鼓極陽而斯竟。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-4a.11">推物奮之將零兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-4a.12">知先業之不競。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-4a.13">何虞舜之垂裳兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-4a.14">歌南薰而解乎。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-4a.15">民慍彼商均之不肖兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-4a.16">歸四海于文命。」<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-5a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-5a" ed="CHANT" n="002-5a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-5a.2">涼風</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-5a.3">起自朱天編駒之白門/從西南來。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-5a.4">陳子聞而賦之曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-5a.5">「噫涼風之率至兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-5a.6">氣沈奪而趨悴。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-5a.7">景瑟瑟其悉予兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-5a.8">溥白露于唐砌。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-5a.9">憶樂遊之嘉會兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-5a.10">極南州之鴻士。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-5a.11">惜異物之奄迫兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-5a.12">漸一身以媚世。」<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-6a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-6a" ed="CHANT" n="002-6a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-6a.2">閶闔風</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-6a.3">一曰盲風，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-6a.4">又曰飂風，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-6a.5">亦曰泰風。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-6a.6">起自成天之閶闔門。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-6a.7">從西方來。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-6a.8">陳子聞而賦之曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-6a.9">「噫盲風之𩗱𩙖兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-6a.10">闔萬品于黃泉。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-6a.11">悲草木之蘦落兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-6a.12">感生事之暮年。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-6a.13">將憑衰而遄隕兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-6a.14">見神靈之無顏。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-6a.15">聊仙桂以自佩兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-6a.16">掇芳菊以為飱。」<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-7a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-7a" ed="CHANT" n="002-7a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-7a.2">不周風</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-7a.3">一曰麗風。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-7a.4">起自幽天幽都之門。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-7a.5">從西北來。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-7a.6">陳子聞而賦之曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-7a.7">「噫肅肅之不周兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-7a.8">哀有生之盡劉。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-7a.9">氣感發而襲予室兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-7a.10">塗版屋以綢繆。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-7a.11">追孩提之官處兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-7a.12">隱雙闕之廣修。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-7a.13">去傳舍之無幾兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-7a.14">恣麋鹿之所遊。」<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-8a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-8a" ed="CHANT" n="002-8a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-8a.2">廣莫風</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-8a.3">一曰寒風，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-8a.4">又曰涼風。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-8a.5">起自玄天之寒門。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-8a.6">從北方來。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-8a.7">陳子聞而賦之曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-8a.8">「噫！<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-8a.9">廣莫之蓬蓬兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-8a.10">負一陽而上舒。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-8a.11">則先王之閉關兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-8a.12">衷紛濁其焉驅。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-8a.13">厲晏歲之冰雪兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-8a.14">攬無溫之故襦。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-8a.15">閱慈母之手澤兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-8a.16">痛罔極以躊躕。」<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-9a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-9a" ed="CHANT" n="002-9a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-9a.2">雷</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-9a.3">陰陽相薄而為雷，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-9a.4">天地之鼓也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-9a.5">陳子聞而賦之曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-9a.6">「來殷殷以疾舉兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-9a.7">撼坤維而崩蕩。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-9a.8">鼓含生以長遂兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-9a.9">慨必壯之永降。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-9a.10">彼君子之修省兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-9a.11">奉天威以寅亮。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-9a.12">唯狡童之不戒兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-9a.13">乃終喪乎七鬯。」<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-10a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-10a" ed="CHANT" n="002-10a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-10a.2">雨</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-10a.3">陰陽相蒸為雨。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-10a.4">陳子聞而賦之曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-10a.5">「惟太陰之次畢兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-10a.6">乘玄雲之祁祁。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-10a.7">衡君德之狂肅兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-10a.8">乃或恒而或時。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-10a.9">滅燭龍之偉耀兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-10a.10">動子桑之歔。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-10a.11">欷驚南冠之長往兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-10a.12">為土偶之所嗤。」<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-11a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-11a" ed="CHANT" n="002-11a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-11a.2">霰</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-11a.3">一曰霄雪。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-11a.4">水雪雜下也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-11a.5">雪自上下，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-11a.6">為溫氣所摶，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-11a.7">故曰陽之專氣為霰。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-11a.8">陳子聞而賦之曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-11a.9">「瀌廻霰之雜遝兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-11a.10">遡流風而逸起。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-11a.11">詠雨雪之遺旨兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-11a.12">年既邁乎三紀。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-11a.13">慚不惑之予遠兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-11a.14">毛班班而齲齒。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-11a.15">聊飲酒以胥會兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-11a.16">悼親戚之無幾。」<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-12a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-12a" ed="CHANT" n="002-12a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-12a.2">雹</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-12a.3">霰之流也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-12a.4">陰氣暴上，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-12a.5">雨則凝結成雹。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-12a.6">故曰陰之專氣為雹。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-12a.7">陳子聞而賦之曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-12a.8">「驅驚頹以下降兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-12a.9">躍冰丸以破屋。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-12a.10">摧麰麥之方振兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-12a.11">殺既拆之荏菽。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-12a.12">縣枵腹以待哺兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-12a.13">畯夫告言以有蹙。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-12a.14">豈天誤予之負名兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-12a.15">戒予食夫周粟。」<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-13a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-13a" ed="CHANT" n="002-13a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-13a.2">雪</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-13a.3">水下遇寒而凝，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-13a.4">因風相襲，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-13a.5">而成雪也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-13a.6">陳子聞而賦之曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-13a.7">「紛玄液之上凝兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-13a.8">色杲杲而返母。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-13a.9">似飛鹺之高撒兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-13a.10">扣霏屑於蓬牗。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-13a.11">豈焦舌之莫辨兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-13a.12">實病聰之所咎。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-13a.13">弛昔余之桑土兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-13a.14">瞻玉樹而長詬。」<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-14a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-14a" ed="CHANT" n="002-14a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-14a.2">餘溜</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-14a.3">雨後簷溝餘瀝也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-14a.4">陳子聞而賦之曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-14a.5">「瞻霂霡之霏微兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-14a.6">染陶瓦以驟濕。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-14a.7">瀝洪滋於方至兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-14a.8">繼餘潤而晚及。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-14a.9">挾鳴漏以霄下兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-14a.10">和孤婺之夜泣。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-14a.11">擊愁心之欲碎兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_002-14a.12">弄甘焦以點滴。」<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
<div><head>籟紀．天籟卷之中</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-1a" ed="CHANT" n="003-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-1a.2">野哭</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-1a.3">野哭者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-1a.4">死喪離別，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-1a.5">激於中而發也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-1a.6">陳子聞而賦之曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-1a.7">「聲慛慛以激子兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-1a.8">來莫知其誰氏。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-1a.9">鬱悲音以乍斷兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-1a.10">振餘傷而復起。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-1a.11">將勾踐之去國兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-1a.12">抑哀姜之過市。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-1a.13">懷江南以隕涕兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-1a.14">壯包胥於泉裏。」<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-2a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-2a" ed="CHANT" n="003-2a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-2a.2">聞嘆</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-2a.3">聞嘆者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-2a.4">聞人之嗟嘆聲也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-2a.5">陳子聞而賦之曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-2a.6">「夜蕭寂以澄予聽兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-2a.7">聆有喟之嘆音。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-2a.8">知時運之多紛繆兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-2a.9">昧陰陽之有屈伸。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-2a.10">置彼樞之不可奪兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-2a.11">俟我生之有辰。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-2a.12">欲尋聲而遠慰兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-2a.13">故再三而莫禁。」<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-3a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-3a" ed="CHANT" n="003-3a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-3a.2">孤嘯</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-3a.3">嘯，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-3a.4">吹聲也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-3a.5">又蹙口出聲也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-3a.6">陳子聞而賦之曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-3a.7">「軋喉舌之妙響兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-3a.8">寫清啇於天表。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-3a.9">闢流雲之既合兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-3a.10">落驚禽於枝杪。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-3a.11">洵魯女之憂懷兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-3a.12">動傍人之嗟悼。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-3a.13">將倚柱以循和兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-3a.14">為孰少而孰老。」<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-4a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-4a" ed="CHANT" n="003-4a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-4a.2">市譁</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-4a.3">市譁者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-4a.4">來城郭競市之喧囂也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-4a.5">陳子聞而賦之曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-4a.6">「喧新豐之雞犬兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-4a.7">謼咸陽之大賈。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-4a.8">爭魚鹽之湧集兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-4a.9">望繒粟而遙赴。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-4a.10">朝摩肩以有求兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-4a.11">夕掉臂而不顧。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-4a.12">恐五尺之見欺兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-4a.13">懼三人之多虎。」<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-5a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-5a" ed="CHANT" n="003-5a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-5a.2">村唱</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-5a.3">村唱者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-5a.4">村落之謳吟，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-5a.5">里巷之聲調也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-5a.6">陳子聞而賦之曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-5a.7">「噫頹曜之既匿兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-5a.8">紛下來之牛羊。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-5a.9">乘籬落之烟火兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-5a.10">出嗚嗚之韻揚。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-5a.11">歸南山之種荳兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-5a.12">起陌上之採桑。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-5a.13">痛貞良之摧損兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-5a.14">悲淫佚之抵亡。」<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-6a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-6a" ed="CHANT" n="003-6a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-6a.2">宵舂</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-6a.3">宵舂者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-6a.4">民家夜碓杵臼之聲也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-6a.5">陳子聞而賦之曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-6a.6">「協動止於大易兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-6a.7">驗凶豐於象垣。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-6a.8">運長築以宵振兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-6a.9">激飛輪以夜翻。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-6a.10">擣飢腸以欲絕兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-6a.11">驚饞夢之幻飡。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-6a.12">懷斗粟之悲歌兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-6a.13">怪亡人之見殘。」<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-7a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-7a" ed="CHANT" n="003-7a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-7a.2">夜織</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-7a.3">夜織者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-7a.4">閨中機杼之聲也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-7a.5">陳子聞而賦之曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-7a.6">「有空閨之婺婦兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-7a.7">畏秋衾之夜長。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-7a.8">躍奔梭以吐霧兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-7a.9">轉鳴柚而捲霜。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-7a.10">聲幽軋以若訴兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-7a.11">見靡他之衷腸。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-7a.12">謂君子之永逝兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-7a.13">將為誰之衣裳。」<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-8a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-8a" ed="CHANT" n="003-8a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-8a.2">擣衣</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-8a.3">擣衣者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-8a.4">秋深治衣之聲也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-8a.5">陳子聞而賦之曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-8a.6">「陟涼颷之發發兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-8a.7">&amp;CH-0F01B9;秋砧之微微。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-8a.8">振木葉於將墜兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-8a.9">挾哀音而下飛。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-8a.10">摧壯遊之行色兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-8a.11">怯關河之舊衣。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-8a.12">寧溝壑以自處兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-8a.13">無綈袍之故知。」<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-9a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-9a" ed="CHANT" n="003-9a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-9a.2">城柝</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-9a.3">城柝者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-9a.4">邏卒之柝聲也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-9a.5">陳子聞而賦之曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-9a.6">「崔危堞之拂雲兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-9a.7">戒鳴柝之宵厲。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-9a.8">引飄風以忽遠兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-9a.9">雜零雨而聚至。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-9a.10">驅暴客以遐遁兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-9a.11">閔征夫之勞勩。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-9a.12">宜五丈之莫犯兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-9a.13">何城門之不閉。」<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-10a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-10a" ed="CHANT" n="003-10a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-10a.2">戍鼓</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-10a.3">戍鼓者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-10a.4">郡縣嚴更之鼓聲也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-10a.5">陳子聞而賦之曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-10a.6">「𪔳徐徐其繹奏兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-10a.7">訇沉沉其倦數。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-10a.8">燈含陰以將滅兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-10a.9">扄千門而萬戶。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-10a.10">憂方謝而復振兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-10a.11">節嘻吁於將度。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-10a.12">憐羈魂之未寤兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-10a.13">謂朝陽之禁鼓。」<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-11a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-11a" ed="CHANT" n="003-11a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-11a.2">昏鐘</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-11a.3">昏鍾者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-11a.4">節蚤夜之鍾聲也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-11a.5">陳子聞而賦之曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-11a.6">「警宵晨之代謝兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-11a.7">宣鳧垂之令音。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-11a.8">載白月以遙度兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-11a.9">隔層霜而遠聞。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-11a.10">雖虛受以如響兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-11a.11">非寸&amp;CH-0F0228;之可因。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-11a.12">謂君子之有思兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-11a.13">如賣降之武臣。」<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-12a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-12a" ed="CHANT" n="003-12a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-12a.2">巷笛</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-12a.3">巷笛者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-12a.4">村巷吹笛聲也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-12a.5">陳子聞而賦之曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-12a.6">「志噎鬱其無歡兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-12a.7">步躅蹐而登樓。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-12a.8">聲惋惋其愁予兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-12a.9">灑芳音而漫流。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-12a.10">長關山之白髮兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-12a.11">來城闕之素秋。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-12a.12">臨悲風而悵望兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-12a.13">懷故國以多憂。」<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-13a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-13a" ed="CHANT" n="003-13a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-13a.2">邊笳</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-13a.3">邊笳者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-13a.4">胡人捲蘆葉吹之作聲也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-13a.5">陳子聞而賦之曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-13a.6">「渺長河之落日兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-13a.7">天沉沉而奏笳。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-13a.8">摧陰山之白草兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-13a.9">裂黃雲而捲沙。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-13a.10">泣將軍之降鬼兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-13a.11">興蔡女之咨嗟。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-13a.12">既大節之莫救兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-13a.13">又奚言之足嘉。」<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-14a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-14a" ed="CHANT" n="003-14a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-14a.2">歸輪</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-14a.3">歸輪者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-14a.4">驅車之聲也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-14a.5">陳子聞而賦之曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-14a.6">「亘修途以欲暮兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-14a.7">野遼敻其無人。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-14a.8">翻轔轔以言邁兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-14a.9">奏孤征之兩輪。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-14a.10">憮勞音之既遠兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-14a.11">望平原之暗塵。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-14a.12">恐未路之嶮巇兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-14a.13">展沖沖之我心。」<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-15a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-15a" ed="CHANT" n="003-15a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-15a.2">鳴楫</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-15a.3">鳴楫者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-15a.4">操舟之楫聲也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-15a.5">陳子聞而賦之曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-15a.6">「睇川河以既淼兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-15a.7">蕩鳴楫而何之。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-15a.8">破秋萍於欲聚兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-15a.9">鼓文浪而迴堤。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-15a.10">笑罔水可行舟兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-15a.11">昧陸海之無涯。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-15a.12">起風波於四顧兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_003-15a.13">徒臨流而汝思。」<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
<div><head>籟紀．天籟卷之下</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-1a" ed="CHANT" n="004-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-1a.2">灘聲</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-1a.3">陳子聞而賦之曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-1a.4">「怒廻岸以若抗兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-1a.5">扼飛源於上游。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-1a.6">迸哀瀧而奔瀉兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-1a.7">逝滔滔其莫休。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-1a.8">聲潺湲以擊予枕兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-1a.9">魂氾淚而欲流。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-1a.10">謂靈均之彷彿兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-1a.11">寤須臾之足羞。」<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-2a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-2a" ed="CHANT" n="004-2a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-2a.2">谷聲</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-2a.3">谷聲者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-2a.4">虛谷接物之聲也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-2a.5">陳子聞而賦之曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-2a.6">「抱紆岡以貯響兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-2a.7">副有聲而和旃。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-2a.8">鳥嚶嚶其效苦兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-2a.9">風凄凄而愈嚴。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-2a.10">輔孤臣以太息兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-2a.11">偕怨女而告天。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-2a.12">酬虛空之謦欬兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-2a.13">慰山鬼之笑言。」<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-3a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-3a" ed="CHANT" n="004-3a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-3a.2">林聲</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-3a.3">林聲者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-3a.4">林木和風之聲也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-3a.5">陳子聞而賦之曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-3a.6">「森高林以藐邃兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-3a.7">感吹萬而怒號。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-3a.8">震晴空之雷雨兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-3a.9">磕陸野之洶濤。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-3a.10">雖美惡之同風兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-3a.11">諒貞糜之異操。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-3a.12">憂樗櫟之偕朽兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-3a.13">羨松柏之後凋。」<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-4a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-4a" ed="CHANT" n="004-4a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-4a.2">落葉聲</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-4a.3">落葉聲者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-4a.4">木葉脫落聲也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-4a.5">陳子聞而賦之曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-4a.6">「既霜露以申戒兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-4a.7">復寒風以見摧。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-4a.8">寔衰運之伊遘兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-4a.9">匪故條之忍辭。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-4a.10">約閨容以並落兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-4a.11">引鄉心而共飛。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-4a.12">翻芳華於回首兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-4a.13">嘆飄泊其焉依。」<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-5a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-5a" ed="CHANT" n="004-5a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-5a.2">雞聲</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-5a.3">雞聲者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-5a.4">陽將升，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-5a.5">雞感之而為聲也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-5a.6">陳子聞而賦之曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-5a.7">「知曜靈之將曙兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-5a.8">度芳聲於夜塒。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-5a.9">動征車於前路兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-5a.10">送孤舟於天涯。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-5a.11">衣顛倒以振予袖兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-5a.12">愴河山之已非。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-5a.13">念牝晨之凶索兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-5a.14">又焉思乎后妃。」<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-6a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-6a" ed="CHANT" n="004-6a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-6a.2">蛙聲</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-6a.3">蛙聲者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-6a.4">沮澤之鳴蛙也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-6a.5">陳子聞而賦之曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-6a.6">「鬱葭菼以被野兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-6a.7">欲颺灰其無從。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-6a.8">都沮洳以為勝兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-6a.9">擅長鳴以稱雄。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-6a.10">嗟子陽之尊大兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-6a.11">感華林之太惷。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-6a.12">予微茲之故兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-6a.13">胡為乎泥中。」<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-7a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-7a" ed="CHANT" n="004-7a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-7a.2">子鵑</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-7a.3">一名雋周，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-7a.4">蜀鳥也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-7a.5">今在處有之。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-7a.6">陳子聞而賦之曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-7a.7">「當仲陽之方茂兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-7a.8">美百草之奮興。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-7a.9">哀秦隴之多客兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-7a.10">怪雋周之夜鳴。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-7a.11">動繁情於中歲兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-7a.12">墮纖月於荒城。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-7a.13">雖開明之克聖兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-7a.14">能無傷乎此聲。」<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-8a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-8a" ed="CHANT" n="004-8a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-8a.2">猨聲</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-8a.3">猨聲者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-8a.4">啼猨聲也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-8a.5">陳子聞而賦之曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-8a.6">「夜悠永以無際兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-8a.7">扄空山之闃寂。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-8a.8">揚悲音於林杪兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-8a.9">裂崇岡而四出。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-8a.10">豈南征之君子兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-8a.11">哀故軀之莫得。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-8a.12">知變化之非類兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-8a.13">宜安夫運之所值。」<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-9a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-9a" ed="CHANT" n="004-9a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-9a.2">蟬聲</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-9a.3">一曰蜩螗，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-9a.4">通謂之蟬。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-9a.5">陳子聞而賦之曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-9a.6">「謝糞壤以沖舉兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-9a.7">登高枝以優游。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-9a.8">飲清露以自滋兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-9a.9">睨萬物以焉求。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-9a.10">惡芳聲之莫振兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-9a.11">詎無舌而少休。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-9a.12">恐字螳螂之奄至兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-9a.13">豈惟限乎春秋。」<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-10a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-10a" ed="CHANT" n="004-10a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-10a.2">蟋蟀聲</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-10a.3">菴也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-10a.4">一名促織。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-10a.5">陳子聞而賦之曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-10a.6">「虛白月於秋除兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-10a.7">避零露干宵徑。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-10a.8">既升堂以入室兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-10a.9">復同聲而相應。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-10a.10">此云息而彼興兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-10a.11">寐欲成而還聽。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-10a.12">歎杼柚之多空兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-10a.13">雖懶婦其何病。」<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-11a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-11a" ed="CHANT" n="004-11a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-11a.2">鴈聲</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-11a.3">一曰陽鳥。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-11a.4">陳子聞而賦之曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-11a.5">「度秋風於絕塞兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-11a.6">審厥居於彭蠡。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-11a.7">雲垂垂其天遠兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-11a.8">嘆孤征而莫止。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-11a.9">既銜蘆以似智兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-11a.10">何不材而取死。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-11a.11">羨冥冥之高舉兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-11a.12">嗤弋人之慕爾。」<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-12a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-12a" ed="CHANT" n="004-12a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-12a.2">烏聲</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-12a.3">一曰蜀山鳥。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-12a.4">陳子聞而賦之曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-12a.5">「麗玄形於赤日兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-12a.6">受靈質於瑤星。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-12a.7">願推愛於君子兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-12a.8">母取訾於一鳴。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-12a.9">慨雞鶩不可與爭食兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-12a.10">悼危巢之未足以寧。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-12a.11">懷反哺之大義兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-12a.12">曷勝乎予之私情。」<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-13a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-13a" ed="CHANT" n="004-13a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-13a.2">鴟聲</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-13a.3">一曰服鳥。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-13a.4">陳子聞而賦之曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-13a.5">「乘陰風以嘯乎幽薄兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-13a.6">度西堂而來此。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-13a.7">聲擁寒裯而起聽兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-13a.8">驀焉傷夫賈生。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-13a.9">既同死生於不較兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-13a.10">恐有言之未能知。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-13a.11">響不為惡聲美兮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1660_CHANT_004-13a.12">聊寫賦以與賡。<lb/></seg>
</p>
